        "Object": "on the basis of the assessments referred to in paragraph 4, the commission shall adopt guidelines for the implementation of this directive. those guidelines shall include: — criteria and methods for assessing the energy performance of buildings; — requirements for the calculation of primary and final energy consumption; — requirements for the verification of compliance with the minimum energy performance requirements laid down by member states in accordance with article 4(1); — requirements for the provision of information to building owners or occupiers on the energy performance of buildings; — criteria and methods for assessing the energy performance of building elements, components and systems; — criteria and methods for assessing the energy performance of new and existing heating and cooling systems; — criteria and methods for assessing the energy performance of windows, doors and other openings; — requirements for the provision of information to manufacturers or suppliers on the energy performance of building products."
