If you intended to ask a specific question or request information about this topic, please clarify. Otherwise, if the repetition was unintentional, here is a summarized version:

The Commission is empowered to amend the regulation by adapting formulae set out in Annex I using methodology adopted pursuant to paragraph 7 of Article 15. This amendment ensures that reduction requirements are of comparable stringency for manufacturers and vehicles of different utility under both old and new test procedures.

If you need more detailed information or have a specific question related to this, feel free to ask!

